item.dc:creator: @rockh4rd rockh4rd
item.description:
@rockh4rd wrote:

[quote=“Gh0stb4rr4g3, post:2, topic:229000”]Did you downloaded JDK yet ?

If yes right click the .bat file and go to edit and look for the Java Version.

Like this:

[code]@echo off
color 0a
title Ghostscape
java -Xmx512m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.08-ga-bin.jar server[code]

java-3.0.08 Is the version

Just change it if it wont work.[/code][/code][/quote]

i got jdk 7
